                    <li>Select Company Name</li>
                  <li>Draft MOA and AOA</li>
                    <li>Submit SPICe+ Form</li>
                    <li>MCA Verification</li>
                    <LI>Issuance of COI</LI>
                  </ul>
                  </td>
                </tr>
